title: Post-Fight.Press.Conference.for.UFC.152 -  MMA.Know.It.Alls
description:
MMA Know-It-Alls Presents:

                   The Official UFC 152 Post Fight Press Conference



Sep 23, 2012 - TORONTO 


At the UFC 152 post-fight press conference, Dana White is critical of fans who didn't 

like the UFC flyweight title fight and calls out a local writer. Also, Jon Jones 

discusses his injury, his performance and much more.
